---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout>
  <nav
    class="fixed top-0 left-0 right-0 z-40 bg-violet-200/70 backdrop-blur-xl border-b border-violet-100/80"
  >
    <div
      class="max-w-4xl mx-auto flex flex-wrap items-center gap-x-3 gap-y-2 md:gap-y-1.5 px-6 py-2.5"
    >
      <a
        href="#top"
        class="px-3.5 py-1.5 rounded-full text-[0.7rem] md:text-xs lg:text-sm font-semibold text-indigo-900/85 hover:text-indigo-950 hover:bg-indigo-50 hover:shadow-[0_8px_24px_rgba(165,180,252,0.9)] hover:-translate-y-[1px] transition-all duration-200 ease-out"
      >
        Home
      </a>
      <a
        href="#about"
        class="px-3.5 py-1.5 rounded-full text-[0.7rem] md:text-xs lg:text-sm font-semibold text-indigo-900/85 hover:text-indigo-950 hover:bg-indigo-50 hover:shadow-[0_8px_24px_rgba(165,180,252,0.9)] hover:-translate-y-[1px] transition-all duration-200 ease-out"
      >
        The Architect
      </a>
      <a
        href="#relationships"
        class="px-3.5 py-1.5 rounded-full text-[0.7rem] md:text-xs lg:text-sm font-semibold text-indigo-900/85 hover:text-indigo-950 hover:bg-pink-50 hover:shadow-[0_8px_24px_rgba(251,207,232,0.9)] hover:-translate-y-[1px] transition-all duration-200 ease-out"
      >
        Relationship Coaching
      </a>
      <a
        href="#lab"
        class="px-3.5 py-1.5 rounded-full text-[0.7rem] md:text-xs lg:text-sm font-semibold text-indigo-900/85 hover:text-indigo-950 hover:bg-emerald-50 hover:shadow-[0_8px_24px_rgba(167,243,208,0.9)] hover:-translate-y-[1px] transition-all duration-200 ease-out"
      >
        The AI Lab &amp; Studio
      </a>
      <a
        href="#fatherhood"
        class="px-3.5 py-1.5 rounded-full text-[0.7rem] md:text-xs lg:text-sm font-semibold text-indigo-900/85 hover:text-indigo-950 hover:bg-amber-50 hover:shadow-[0_8px_24px_rgba(253,230,138,0.9)] hover:-translate-y-[1px] transition-all duration-200 ease-out"
      >
        Fatherhood
      </a>
      <a
        href="#contact"
        class="px-3.5 py-1.5 rounded-full text-[0.7rem] md:text-xs lg:text-sm font-semibold text-indigo-900/85 hover:text-indigo-950 hover:bg-violet-50 hover:shadow-[0_8px_24px_rgba(196,181,253,0.9)] hover:-translate-y-[1px] transition-all duration-200 ease-out"
      >
        Connect
      </a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <div class="pt-20 md:pt-24 px-6">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl">
      <header
        class="relative text-left py-16 md:py-20"
      >
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-white/65 backdrop-blur-2xl border-b border-violet-100/50"></div>
      <div class="relative max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
        <p class="text-[0.7rem] uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-indigo-700/90 mb-4">
          Systems of the Heart, Sound &amp; Code
        </p>
        <h1
          class="text-[2.4rem] md:text-[3.1rem] leading-tight font-semibold text-indigo-950/90 drop-shadow-sm"
        >
          JoySomatic
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-4 text-base md:text-lg text-indigo-900/85 max-w-none">
          Decoding the language of the Body, Relationships, and Systems through somatics,
          sound, and engineering.
        </p>
      </div>
      </header>

      <main class="pb-16">
    <section id="about" class="mt-12 md:mt-16">
      <h2
        class="inline-block text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-indigo-950/90 border-b border-pink-200 pb-1"
      >
        Hi, I’m José.
      </h2>

      <div class="mt-6 space-y-4 text-base md:text-lg text-indigo-900/90">
        <p>
          Born in <strong>1982</strong>, my journey into healing began as a teenager, driven by
          the weight of intense anxiety. I later realized I was a
          <strong>Highly Sensitive child</strong>—born with a deep empathy and intuition that I’ve
          spent the last two decades learning to navigate through therapy, somatic practices, and
          lived experience.
        </p>

        <p>
          Since <strong>2022</strong>, I have navigated the rhythms of co-parenting. This journey
          of humility has been my greatest teacher in presence and nervous system regulation. Now,
          as I enter this next chapter, I am
          <strong>re-activating my roots as a Developer and Sound Engineer</strong>.
        </p>

        <p>
          After a significant hiatus to focus on family, I am back at the keyboard and in the
          studio. I am currently "building in public," documenting my return to code and audio
          engineering as I merge these technical worlds with my somatic coaching practice.
        </p>

        <blockquote class="border-l-4 border-pink-200 pl-4 italic text-indigo-900/85">
          "I am currently re-coding my life and my tools. I look at life through two lenses: the
          <strong>Somatic heart</strong> that feels the rhythm, and the
          <strong>Engineer’s mind</strong> that understands the system. I’m finding the signal in
          the noise, one line of code at a time."
        </blockquote>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="relationships" class="mt-12 md:mt-16">
      <h2
        class="inline-block text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-indigo-950/90 border-b border-pink-200 pb-1"
      >
        Relationship &amp; Somatic Coaching
      </h2>

      <p class="mt-6 text-base md:text-lg text-indigo-900/90">
        My primary energy is dedicated to helping people navigate the complexities of human
        connection. I help individuals and couples "debug" the patterns that keep them stuck,
        using the body as our primary source of truth.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-8 space-y-4 md:space-y-6">
        <div class="rounded-[2.25rem] bg-white/90 shadow-[0_18px_45px_rgba(148,163,184,0.5)] px-5 py-5">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-indigo-950/90">Relational Insight</h3>
          <p class="mt-2.5 text-sm md:text-base text-indigo-900/85">
            We look at the <strong>System</strong> of your relationship. I help you identify the
            "phase cancellation" in your communication—the moments where you clash instead of
            harmonize—and help you rewrite those scripts for deeper connection.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-[2.25rem] bg-white/90 shadow-[0_18px_45px_rgba(148,163,184,0.5)] px-5 py-5">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-indigo-950/90">
            In-Person Sessions (Safe Spaces)
          </h3>
          <p class="mt-2.5 text-sm md:text-base text-indigo-900/85">
            I believe healing happens best where you feel most grounded. In-person sessions can be
            held in <strong>nature, a private home, or any quiet space</strong> that feels safe and
            supportive for you. Removing the clinical office environment allows the nervous system
            to open in its own time.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-[2.25rem] bg-white/90 shadow-[0_18px_45px_rgba(148,163,184,0.5)] px-5 py-5">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-indigo-950/90">
            Remote &amp; Async Coaching (Available to All)
          </h3>
          <p class="mt-2.5 text-sm md:text-base text-indigo-900/85">
            Presence isn't limited by geography. I offer
            <strong>Virtual Meetings (Google Meet)</strong> and
            <strong>Asynchronous Voice Coaching</strong> for everyone—whether you are across the
            world or just prefer to process your growth from the comfort of your own space.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="lab" class="mt-12 md:mt-16">
      <h2
        class="inline-block text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-indigo-950/90 border-b border-pink-200 pb-1"
      >
        The JoySomatic Lab: Building in Public
      </h2>
    
      <ul class="mt-6 list-disc pl-5 space-y-4 text-base md:text-lg text-indigo-900/90">
        <li>
          <strong>The Journey Back:</strong> You can follow my progress on <strong>GitHub</strong> 
          as I refresh my Python skills and explore the latest in AI-native development.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>The Wisdom Synthesis Engine:</strong> My current project is a local-first tool 
          designed to extract high-signal insights from long-form YouTube and audio content. 
          To respect data sovereignty and copyright, this framework is built to be <strong>downloaded 
          and executed locally</strong> for personal research.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Signal over Noise:</strong> The engine automates transcription and segmentation, 
          generating structured <strong>PDF summaries</strong> and high-fidelity <strong>audio snippets</strong> 
          to turn digital content into actionable somatic wisdom.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Sound Engineering:</strong> I continue to offer high-resolution audio production 
          for local artists, bringing an engineer's ear to every frequency.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section id="fatherhood" class="mt-12 md:mt-16">
      <h2
        class="inline-block text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-indigo-950/90 border-b border-pink-200 pb-1"
      >
        Parenting &amp; Conscious Leadership
      </h2>

      <p class="mt-6 text-base md:text-lg text-indigo-900/90">
        Navigating a 50/50 co-parenting partnership while managing a career pivot is my daily practice. I offer a unique
        perspective for fathers who feel the weight of responsibility and want to lead their
        families with presence rather than pressure.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section id="contact" class="mt-12 md:mt-16">
      <h2
        class="inline-block text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-indigo-950/90 border-b border-pink-200 pb-1"
      >
        Work With Me
      </h2>

      <div class="mt-6 space-y-4 text-base md:text-lg text-indigo-900/90">
        <p class="max-w-none">
          I am available for limited 1:1 coaching, sound production, and technical collaborations.
        </p>
        <p class="max-w-none">
          Email:
          <a
            href="mailto:joysomatic@gmail.com"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full px-5 py-2.5 text-sm md:text-base font-semibold text-indigo-900/90 bg-violet-200/60 hover:bg-violet-200/90 hover:shadow-[0_10px_30px_rgba(196,181,253,0.7)] hover:-translate-y-[1px] transition-all duration-200 ease-out"
          >
            joysomatic@gmail.com
          </a>
        </p>
        <p class="space-x-3">
          <a
            href="https://linkedin.com/in/joysomatic"
            target="_blank"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full px-3 py-1.5 text-xs md:text-sm font-semibold text-indigo-900/85 bg-white/70 hover:bg-sky-50 hover:shadow-[0_10px_26px_rgba(59,130,246,0.55)] hover:-translate-y-[1px] transition-all duration-200 ease-out"
          >
            LinkedIn
          </a>
          <span>|</span>
          <a
            href="https://github.com/joysomatic"
            target="_blank"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full px-3 py-1.5 text-xs md:text-sm font-semibold text-indigo-900/85 bg-white/70 hover:bg-indigo-50 hover:shadow-[0_10px_26px_rgba(129,140,248,0.55)] hover:-translate-y-[1px] transition-all duration-200 ease-out"
          >
            GitHub
          </a>
          <span>|</span>
          <a
            href="https://instagram.com/joysomatic"
            target="_blank"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full px-3 py-1.5 text-xs md:text-sm font-semibold text-indigo-900/85 bg-white/70 hover:bg-pink-50 hover:shadow-[0_10px_26px_rgba(244,114,182,0.55)] hover:-translate-y-[1px] transition-all duration-200 ease-out"
          >
            Instagram
          </a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer
    class="mt-16 border-t border-violet-100/80 text-center text-xs md:text-sm text-indigo-900/70 py-6 px-4"
  >
    <p>© 2026 JoySomatic – José Oñate Yáñez | Built with Code &amp; Heart</p>
  </footer>
</BaseLayout>

